  <brief_title>Endotracheal Cardiac Output Monitor (ECOM) for Patients Undergoing Liver Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Noninvasive ECOM Monitoring of Hemodynamic Parameters During Liver Transplantation</official_title>
