  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the endotracheal cardiac output monitor
      (ECOM) is accurate and predictive in liver failure patients with hyperdynamic circulatory
      changes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
